Common.Brochures.Common.BrochureName: Variant2 Brochure - 2466 42nd St N, Fargo, ND.pdf

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: This property is ideally located on the north side of Fargo, ND in an industrial park. The site sits just one mile from the I-29 Interstate via brand new, concrete-paved roads. This location offers extremely close proximity to UPS and FedEx hubs, the BNSF Railroad, Hector International Airport, as well as the new 1.3 Million square foot Amazon distribution center.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE, along with Enclave, are pleased to offer Variant2, a new spec 145,200 SF concrete tilt-up warehouse in Fargo, ND. The property features 30’+ ceilings, 1,000a/480v 3-phase power, and ESFR fire suppression. Loading docks and drive-ins can be built-to-suit with plenty of room for parking and/or building expansion on the 11.2 acres of land.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to offer this 40,026 SF concrete warehouse for sublease in Grand Forks, ND.  The property features three loading docks, four drive-ins and sits on 4.1 acres of land with the ability to expand if necessary.  The current Tenant’s lease term expires January 31, 2024 and the building is available immediately.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
3020 1St Ave W is a large industrial warehouse located just off Highway 2 in 
Williston, ND. The property is 18,057 SF which includes 6,204 SF of office space, 11,853 SF of shop space, and two overhead cranes. The 1.43-acre parcel of land includes 26,000 SF of exterior concrete paving and the yard is fully fenced. Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: We are pleased to offer this rare 5,000 SF industrial space for lease. The space includes approximately 550 SF of offices, a kitchenette, and restrooms including showers and laundry. There is also mezzanine space that can be used for light storage or office space if needed. The warehouse space, approximately 4,450 SF has one large overhead door, one smaller 8' x 10' door, and 3 man doors.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for sublease this 17,500 SF industrial space in Williston, ND. This property has 400 feet of frontage along Highway 85 with heated shop space, four drive-ins, and 1,200 SF of heated and air-conditioned office space with mezzanine above.    
The property is zoned industrial and can be leased as a 7,500 SF suite, 10,000 SF suite, or a 17,500 SF suite. There is a demising wall in-place between the 7,500 SF shop and the 10,000 SF shop/office.  The three-acre parcel of land has 59,000 SF of exterior concrete paving and is easily accessible from two major traffic routes. The building totals 25,000 SF and is currently a multi-tenant building.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer this 19,420 SF industrial property in Williston, ND for sublease. This property has 300 feet of frontage along Highway 85 and consists of two industrial buildings with heated shop space, 6” reinforced concrete floors and 3,276 SF of office space. Building 100 is 10,000 SF with 2,296 SF of office space with mezzanine above and Building 200 is 9,420 SF with 980 SF of office space. 
The 10,000 SF building has four drive-ins with 18’-wide by 17’-high overhead doors and was built in 2008.  The 9,420 SF building has nine drive-ins with 12’-wide by 14’-high overhead doors and was built in 2010.  The yard is fully fenced with a gate entry and there is a 28,000 SF concrete apron and 8,500 SF of asphalt parking.
